 />\n一國一制正式落實</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔通吹風吹到咁行就係出呢招？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂攞正牌入嚟香港平亂<br />\n大家醒水，睇嚟有勢力仲想翻盤 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時，亦有可能係上頭以林鄭下台，<br />\n張建宗作過渡，<br />\n消吓大家嘅氣<br />\n然後，<strong><ins>就沒有然後</ins></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f535c377aad588eb1eeca6fbbe95a350d6d302a9","tid":1367930,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"監警會有用? 點解仲有警黑嘅事件發生? 有無用已經好清楚"},{"pid":"40d4466f769d3054688cca8695be132ef398d5b0","tid":1367930,"uid":265898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"無人收貨牙，食完花生繼727<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSb520H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSb520H.png&h=cd677da0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5131198a75410f9fa750ac27f469e09a113a8a0","tid":1367930,"uid":202269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82e1338a692c4bc5089af564285d2905f934e9a6","tid":1367930,"uid":202269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:41:35.000Z","msg":"道歉有咩用？"},{"pid":"e75198d0544a58ab747171d7cfcbc66dbd5fc96d","tid":1367930,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4293a86d036661f92f4863f764f437515321769e","tid":1367930,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"張建宗代表政府同黑社會割蓆<br />\n政府想Spin去警察做得「不足」，而唔係縱容黑社會襲擊<br />\n只靠監警會調查，可以查到元朗警黑勾結嗎？"},"